            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Bandai 最新推出的 METAL BUILD 系列龙王丸，可说是唤醒了许多 80 后玩家的童年回忆，《魔神英雄传》一向也是小编的童年至爱动画，这部龙神丸复活后的龙王丸，战力大提升亦可以变形凤王形态，Bandai 今次不仅在 METAL BUILD 龙王丸高度还原后，更加入了一些创新设计，可说是 METAL BUILD 系列的一大突破。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258413" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0422-452x580.jpg" alt="" width="452" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0422-452x580.jpg 452w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0422-scaled.jpg 701w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 452px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258414" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0423-465x580.jpg" alt="" width="465" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0423-465x580.jpg 465w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0423-scaled.jpg 722w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 465px" /></p><p>龙王丸本体高约 16cm，横向宽度较大，整体存在感强。重量达 660g，拿在手中颇有份量。涂装方面，电镀金特别出色，天线和肩甲龙纹处呈现出纯净的黄金色泽，灯光照射下极为华丽。值得一提的是，肩甲背面还创新加入了凤凰图案，与前面的龙纹相映成趣；不过头部黑色部份内藏的金龙头，要用强光照射下才可隐约看到，一般的光源只是黑色的一大片，会比较单调。</p><p><a title="_DSC0425" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53941535427/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53941535427_8d6043b4a3_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0425" width="868" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0427" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942686248/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942686248_36b2d7ca90_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0427" width="1022" height="1024" /></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258451" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0820-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0820-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0820-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258428" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0429-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0429-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0429-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258429" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0430-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0430-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0430-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0433-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0433-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0433-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258432" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0434-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0434-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0434-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0435-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0435-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0435-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258434" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0436-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0436-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0436-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258435" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0438-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0438-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0438-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>配件方面，除了一把剑和一面盾牌外，还附带两个替换手型。剑可收纳于盾中，盾牌的 4 片金色羽翼有展开功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258436" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0446-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0446-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0446-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258437" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0447-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0447-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0447-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258438" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0448-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0448-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0448-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258439" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0449-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0449-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0449-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258440" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0450-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0450-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0450-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>头部、肩部、手肘等关节均有不同程度的可动，其中肩部采用二段式关节，内段还使用了齿轮结构，手感不错。腿部关节同样出色，屈膝时膝盖装甲还会联动，细节丰富，不过脚腕的可动性较差，贴地性麻麻地。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258441" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0442-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0442-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0442-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258442" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0439-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0439-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0439-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258443" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0440-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0440-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0440-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258444" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0441-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0441-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0441-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>作为 METAL BUILD 系列首款可变形产品，龙王丸的变形结构可以用精妙来形容。从人形到凤王形态的变形过程，基本还原原作设定，同时加入了很多的心思设计，例如多个连动位置，胸甲、锁链发射器等部位的连动，以及拉出凤王头后，眼神的连动变换。变形后的凤王形态造型优美，但需要支架轮助才可摆设，值得一赞的是，支架接口采用金属材质，大大提升了承重能力和耐用性，之后的 METAL BUILD 的支架都是如此就好了。另外还具备「超凤王」的二段变形，通过展开翅膀、调整尾部等变化，可呈现出更有霸气的姿态，提升了可玩性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258449" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0818-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0818-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0818-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258450" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0819-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0819-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0819-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC0488" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942437546/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942437546_f1bcf12ff1_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0488" width="1024" height="761" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0496" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942770509/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942770509_99718a99ef_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0496" width="1024" height="758" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC0498" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942770669/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942770669_ea0f24ae5d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0498" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258446" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0451-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0451-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0451-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258447" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0452-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0452-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0452-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Action Pose</h2><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0457" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942770534/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942770534_3d00214d76_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0457" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0462" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942893185/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942893185_817813dd28_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0462" width="1024" height="919" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0479" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53941535342/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53941535342_9d6629f617_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0479" width="917" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0484" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942686083/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942686083_4de12b9e33_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0484" width="1024" height="824" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>METAL BUILD 龙王丸无论在涂装品质、把玩体验还是创新设计上，都非常有水准。对于童年回忆的玩家而言，就好像小编那样，其出色的做工和丰富的玩法，实在是非常吸引。</p><p><strong>METAL BUILD DRAGON SCALE 龙王丸</strong><br />
售价：33,000 日圆（含税）<br />
查询：瑞华行</p><p><a title="_DSC0453" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942686203/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942686203_98d561dc4e_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0453" width="1024" height="720" /></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/24/metal-build-ryuoumaru/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/">【评测】METAL BUILD 龙王丸　超凤王二段变形</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
